{
  "stem": "162.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we lived with them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But my mother needed a job.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And she needed to work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And my mother ended up working for a German officers club as a waitress.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As a Pole.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As a Pole, as a waitress.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And that's how we lived there, and that's how we survived for awhile.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember, those were horrible times because the underground in Warsaw and all over Poland was constantly working.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was-- just like there is in Israel today, there were bombings, explosions on the streets.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Some of the Gestapo houses were sabotaged.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "German soldiers walking down the street-- all of a sudden, you're walking down the street, and then you hear gunfire, and a couple of German soldiers were killed on the street.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was very dangerous and not very safe to be.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that's-- I remember my life with my mother and myself.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And towards the end of that, I think I'm missing-- I think maybe I went back again to my grandmother's for awhile.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because I remember I went to my grandmother, and she sent me off on somebody's farm.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I lived on a farm for an awful long time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I remember riding big horses bareback.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I remember walking the fields and-- and playing games with children on this farm, that I lived there for quite awhile.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Still as a Pole.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was in Germany.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When-- when I was in Germany, I was always a German.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When I was in Poland, I was the Stravinsky daughter.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So it was that kind of a thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
